Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起登上回忆的大山——谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个和日向定下的约定实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 下一个约定还在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是饭能纳凉烟火大会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在谷川岳认识的穗香过来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家约好一起看烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常期待的说~但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点道歉啊葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要道歉的是日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵总是怪到我的头上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向才是 不要怪到我头上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 葵的兴趣太灰暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样才不受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个人兴趣你少管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你也一点都不受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受欢迎的事跟现在没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起这事的就是不受欢迎的日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非葵道歉 否则我绝对不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我真是忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(658,212)}再见了 我们的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向那家伙 还不来道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香 欢迎 欢迎来到饭能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从高崎来饭能的路上无聊不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看着景色都觉得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很热呢 不过还好是晴天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小群马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是梦马君哦 心夏很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是饭能银座 对面是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思哦 其实我和日向吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的当然是日向 但她完全都不来道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗 日向她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 雪村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新井老师 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你是几年级的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香是从群马的高崎来这里玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的班主任新井老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 饭能是个很棒的城市哦 请好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆让老师我来带路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始 你都在拍什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧建筑之类的 仓库之类的 很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我看习惯了 什么感觉都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好新鲜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是改变一下视点 看到的景色也会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害呢 穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个糕点店就是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 店里那么忙我还休息 抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 今天你朋友来玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连店长都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得跟你妈妈报告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到饭能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经常来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后来这里聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 之前还在那边的台阶上和日向吵架了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把我的裙子扯下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之后我也把她的裙子扯下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是烟火大会的会场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前 在这里和大家一起吃过饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为日向的错 连我都掉进河里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 我从这架子上摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后就得了恐高症呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 都是日向的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个不关她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是天览山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气好的话 还看得到天空树和富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和日向第一次登上的山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里和日向喝茶 吃三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 总是在说日向的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在饭能 不管去哪里 全都是和日向的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吵架错在她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也有一点点错 稍微道一下歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我去跟她和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 今天请假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 完全没联系我 我什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找葵的话 她今天休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是日向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我常听葵说起你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上可以想象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候掉进沟里什么的 喜欢的人被戳破什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还总是诸多抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑很聪明 很善解人意 不管做什么都很乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多值得学习的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吵架是因为葵不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我也有那么一点点错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 我就稍微道个歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是旧衣服 幸好尺寸合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦到见面的时候 还真难道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我先道歉也会很不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向先来向我道歉就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来 葵应该向我道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香 欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见到枫穿浴衣的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裕香帮我选的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就去祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金鱼小姐 我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是金鱼飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个是金鱼摆尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新月陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攀登龙泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向（葵）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我捞了这么多金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个挑战钓水球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵你们吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没注意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平常没什么变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是那个样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很无聊的小事啦 日向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不是我 是葵吧
